snippet.title: Adventure Kitty: Drill Buster - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Adventure Kitty: Drill Buster is out now on itch.io!
Play the Game Now: https://zaltick.itch.io/adventure-kitty-drill-buster

You can get the soundtrack here: https://zayaltick.bandcamp.com/album/adventure-kitty-drill-buster-part-1-soundtrack

Go for gold and test your risk/reward skills in Adventure Kitty: Drill Buster!
An action paced drill game that has you drilling across new terrains and adapting from your original plan.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZaltickGames
Website: https://drill-buster-site.vercel.app/
TIkTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@zaltickgames
